<br>
<!--EZCODE QUOTE START--><blockquote><b><i>Quote:</i></b><hr> <br>
+9 int is a crap hand item. <br>
Cassius Runeblaze &lt;Avatars of Discord&gt;<br>
lvl 56<br>
Rodcet<br>
<hr></blockquote><!--EZCODE QUOTE END--><br>
<br>
I'm not trying to start a big flame fest; only to educate myself a little.  I've not had the opportunity to turn down items from Sleepers Tomb or Veeshan's Peak as being &quot;too gimpy&quot;, so I haven't seen all the wonderful items that are out there.  <br>
<br>
However, I can only find references to one droppable item over +10 int.  I have a hard time understanding how +9 int could be said to be crap, especially the Glowing Black Stone (which was the item in question) considering it has +10MR.  I have a hard time seeing that as crap.<br>
<br>
Help me understand why my gear is crap.<br>
 <p></p><i></i></td></tr><tr bgcolor=#33333><td nowrap width=20% valign=top align=left><span class=title> <A HREF=http://pub23.ezboard.com/udrednoct.showPublicProfile?language=EN>Drednoct</A></span><br> <span class=usertitle>Forum Apprentice</span><br> <font color=#ffffff>(8/15/01 10:27:07 am)</font><br>    </td><td valign=top align=left class=m><span class=title> Re: equipment question</span><hr size=1> Whoever said that was probably just in a bad mood from camping Pyzjin for a long time and never getting a gbs.<br>
That said, while the +9 int is great, there are other itmes in the game which are easier to get and have better stats (stein of moggok). The gbs is more of a status symbol and just looks kinda cool.<br>
I look at the value of equipment based on my needs. E.g. I would assume someone who does not yet have a hand item and does not have 200+ int would value a +9 int held item very highly whereas someone who already has 200+ int and some other hand item that perhaps give +mana or resists probably wouldn't want something that just gives +9 int as much.<br>
<br>
Drednoct<br>
51 Channeler of the Ebon Legion<br>
Ayonae Ro<br>
 <p></p><i></i></td></tr><tr bgcolor=#000000><td nowrap width=20% valign=top align=left><span class=title> <A HREF=http://pub23.ezboard.com/ulenaddaranatar.showPublicProfile?language=EN>Lenaddar Anatar</A></span><br> <span class=usertitle>Forum Evoker</span><br> <font color=#ffffff>(8/15/01 10:38:05 am)</font><br>    </td><td valign=top align=left class=m><span class=title> Re: equipment question</span><hr size=1> And theres a number of +10 Int items that do make it look a bit course in return.<br>
<br>
For the cash or level challenged theres always the stien of Moggok for 200pp. <br>
<br>
At the high end of goodies thats droppable is the Bioluminesence Orb: +10 Int +8 Str +10 MR/CR/FR +10 mana +10 hps. If I misspelled that item forgive me. Lots of stuff out there if you look. Yes, I have one. It looks just like the GBS, anyways.<br>
<br>
- Len<br>
<br>
 <p>Lenaddar Anatar of Xev
(Lord of Wizardly Gifts from Tolkien) 57th Level Evoker

Chancellor of the Realm
</p><i></i></td></tr><tr bgcolor=#33333><td nowrap width=20% valign=top align=left><span class=title> <A HREF=http://pub23.ezboard.com/ugherad.showPublicProfile?language=EN>Gherad</A></span><br> <span class=usertitle>Forum Evoker</span><br> <font color=#ffffff>(8/15/01 1:06:31 pm)</font><br>    <BR><img src=http://www4.ncsu.edu/~enhoggan/G9.jpg WIDTH=60 HEIGHT=60></td><td valign=top align=left class=m><span class=title> Re: equipment question</span><hr size=1> Your quote seems to come from a level 56 wizard.  High level wizards have too much int as it is.  Many of us can't get below 200int even if we try.  We focus on items with mana, resists, hps, etc.  Int is worthless.<br>
<br>
But 9 int is just fine for a mid level wizard.  I wouldn't worry about it. <p></p><i></i></td></tr></table><table border=0 width=95%><tr><td align=left valign="top"> </td><td align=right valign="top"><a href="http://pub23.ezboard.com/fgraffeswizardcompilationfrm1.showMessage?topicID=6278.topic"> << Prev Topic</a>&nbsp;| <a href="http://pub23.ezboard.com/fgraffeswizardcompilationfrm1.showMessage?topicID=6273.topic"> Next Topic >> </a><br><br></td></tr></table><br><table width=95% border=0><td valign="top"> <a href=http://pub23.ezboard.com/fgraffeswizardcompilationfrm1.emailToFriend?topicID=6270.topic><img src=http://www.ezboard.com/image/email.gif border=0 alt="Email This To a Friend"> Email This To a Friend</a><br> <a href=http://pub23.ezboard.com/fgraffeswizardcompilationfrm1.threadControl?topicID=6270.topic><img src=http://www.ezboard.com/themes/professional/deleteThread.gif border=0 alt="Topic Control Image"> Topic Commands (Moderator only)</a><br> <a href=http://pub23.ezboard.com/fgraffeswizardcompilationfrm1.subscribeUnregisteredToTopic?topicID=6270.topic>Subscribe</a> Click to receive email notification of replies<br>  <a href=http://pub23.ezboard.com/fgraffeswizardcompilationfrm1.unsubscribeUnregisteredToTopic?topicID=6270.topic>Unsubscribe</a> Click to stop receiving email notification of replies<br> </td><td align="right" valign="top"></td></tr><tr align="right"><td colspan=2><form action=http://pub23.ezboard.com/BBSForum.jumpShowForum method=post><table border="0" cellspacing="0" cellpadding="1"><tr><td><b>jump to:</b><select name=forumName><option value="graffeswizardcompilationfrm1">General Discussion<option value="graffeswizardcompilationfrm3">Trade Forum<option value="graffeswizardcompilationfrm4">Rant Forum<option value="graffeswizardcompilationfrm8">Mob Dropped Spells<option value="graffeswizardcompilationfrm10">Class Balance & Class Bugs<option value="graffeswizardcompilationfrm22">Out of Mana<option va